            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.1.0</h2>
<p>Otto now updates itself — it checks once a day and asks before installing anything.</p>
<p>Also fixed: bills no longer warn that a payment is overdue when it was due before you started tracking it, and the day-of-month field now accepts typed numbers instead of only plus and minus clicks.</p>
]]></description>
